{"title":"井冈山是革命山","authors":["文莽彦"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山是革命山\t文莽彦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年前井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆红旗冲九天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农红军闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒豪绅又分田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要保人民坐江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年后井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部大军进深山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要改穷山和恶水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄桐绿茶种上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云山雾海开梯田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业大军万万千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑遍山下十三县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年铁牛跃出土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县县矿苗都露面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四千个铁厂把铁炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山是革命山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它为革命意志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年南瓜大米为红军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今遍地财宝都贡献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出钢铁五十亿（吨），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国见了也傻眼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}